Package org.eclipse.mat.inspections.collections Description

These are queries for Collection classes. The queries delivered with Memory Analyzer and their expected parameters are not part of the API. Both names/identifiers and parameters may change. Subject to that caveat, SnapshotQuery can be used to call these queries.
